      "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Australian Nepalese Multicultural Center (ANMC) is currently looking for a \"Member Service Officer (MSO).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The purpose of this role to provide a range of services to members of Australian Nepalese Multicultural Centre (ANMC) and support Executive Committee and sub-committees for executing its set goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reporting to the Treasurer/President/Secretary, the MSO will be required to assist in a wide range of functions with an emphasis on management of members‚Äô account in recognized accounting software; maintaining members register, follow up of unpaid membership fees/pledged amount, handling enquires and assist Executive Committee and various sub-committees on membership drive, and fundraising campaign.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is a role that requires a capable, self-motivated person with a passion to work in a community-based organization.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please refer to PD for more details.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {\"id\":588,\"href\":\"https://anmcinc.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/PD-_Member-service-officer.pdf\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a href=\"https://anmcinc.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/PD-_Member-service-officer.pdf\">Position Description - ANMC Member service officer</a><a href=\"https://anmcinc.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/PD-_Member-service-officer.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download>Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->",
